{"name": "What If We Kiss to Break the Tension 1/3", "description": "What If We Kiss To Break the Tension?
What if a reckless action triggers the future?
What are the possible realities? 
What happens when our existence breaks? 

This is the first track from my upcoming mixtape, Romance + Rebellion. The mixtape is a collection of tracks that blend my penchant for experimental musical elements with my love for pop, hyperpop and J-core music that I had been consuming. It is what I call effervescent glitch future club music. 

Each edition of this NFT comes with a different piece of digital artwork that accompanies the music, making each NFT truly unique. Besides the unique artwork, other utilities include downloadable stems and remix copyrights; and early access to a live performance video of the song.

More info at https://lalka.online/wiwktbtt-info/ 

Track Name: What If We Kiss To Break The Tension?
Written, Produced, Mixed & Performed by: LCLKA
Mastered by: Becki Whitton
